panels.content: Below is a dashboard intended to visualize the composition of the extracted weapons dataset.  The dashboard is organized first by rows, and then by panels.  In the second row you will find the _TIME WINDOW_ and _SEARCH_ panels, both of which apply global filters to the entire dashboard.  Currently the _TIME WINDOW_ panel is set to filter on the 'indexedAt' field, as all records have a value for that field.  The _GLOBAL FILTERS_ panel on the third row explicitly lists all global filters currently applied to the dashboard.  The _HITS_ type panels generally show the number of records that have a value for a particular field.
panels.title: OVERVIEW
